        <updateDate>2021-09-13T14:15:16Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Expeditious Vaccine Advice with Legitimate, Unbiased, Apolitical, and Technical Expertise Act or the EVALUATE Act</b> </p> <p>This bill requires the Food and Drug Administration, before licensing or authorizing any COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) vaccine, to receive advisory committee recommendations concerning the vaccine's safety and effectiveness.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
